reviewText:
Great documentary. It's not blu-ray but the visual quality still holds up well.
Lingers a lot on the colorful fish species which inhabit the reefs. Most other documentaries don't spend as much time on  them.
Dazzling variety of colors and hues.
Horrible narration. Insomnia curing and not nearly inspiring to match the visuals.
very good dvd.well worth the money.. I enjoyed it very much
I think this dvd is the best one I've seen of the Great Barrier Reef. It was worth the money.
